	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/1f6e4cdd2d37.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	(Un)contained by Andyi Liao
</h3>
<p>
	<span></span>这款木质的方盒子像一个野餐盒，它其实是一个工具箱，巧妙地融入了各种厨房小工具。盒子的盖子是一块砧板，里整齐放置了打蛋器和各类刮刀，他们都配套设计了木质把手，颜色统一，可以错位放置，显得简洁干净。当一群人出去野餐时就可以带着它，每人分得一个工具，利于促进合作。<a href="http://www.andyiliao.com/#/uncontained/" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/ff099e5efea4.jpg" width="600" height="389" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/ff3609e62bf6.jpg" width="600" height="628" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/0cfc8fb53090.jpg" width="1080" height="699" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
